-- Applebee's exploring options, including sale
-- 
-- Tue Feb 13, 2007 8:03am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/13/businesspro-applebees-sale-dc-idUSWEN418520070213

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Restaurant company Applebee's 
International Inc. APPB.O said on Tuesday it is exploring 
strategic alternatives, including the possible sale of the 
company. 


  Applebee's said it has hired Citigroup ( C.N ) and Banc of 
America Securities LLC as financial advisers.